	<h3>Developer at Nilex</h3>
	<p><%= link_to("Nilex", "http://www.nilex.se/", :class => "bold") %> is a producer of service management systems. Over the summer I worked as an Android developer, developer of coded UI tests in Visual Studio and performed regular tests on to the web application. This was a great experience for me to understand how to work with such a large-scale system and improving my Android development skills.</p>
	<div style="text-align: center;">
